The '''grav-belt''' was a form of [[Repulsorlift/Legends|repulsorlift]] equipment which could propel beings through the air. [[Jediboh Opera]] actors and actresses used such belts to leap from one side of the stage to the other.<ref name="Peekoine Opera Blues">{{SpaceFantasyGamerCite|88|Peekoine Opera Blues}}</ref>

